data.description: Welcome to this vast 5 bedroom 3 bathroom home located in Bartow, Florida. You are greeted with upgraded features including an open floorplan, tile flooring in all common areas, and nice gratinate countertops in the kitchen. All of the bedrooms have plush carpets and follow a split living floorplan. This property is conveniently located close to attractions, shopping, a quaint little town, and restaurants. Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity to live in the up and coming Bartow area!
